{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KMBDjDZ2rnCCVjDBajuENp","type":"tool_result","content":"  2085→The `verify` phase accounts for 53.7% of all costs ($412.17) and `retro` phase 11.1% ($85.17). Both are inflated by 58 sessions of zero-value repetition.\n  2086→\n  2087→### Action Items\n  2088→\n  2089→| # | Action | Priority |\n  2090→|---|--------|----------|\n  2091→| 1 | **STOP RALPH IMMEDIATELY** — 58 consecutive no-op sessions, ~$50+ wasted on corruption fixes alone | CRITICAL |\n  2092→| 2 | Fix root cause: Ralph must re-read `sprint-state.json` from disk before each write, not use stale in-memory snapshot | HIGH |\n  2093→| 3 | Add circuit breaker: auto-halt after N consecutive sessions with zero productive work | MEDIUM |\n  2094→\n  2095→### Bottom Line\n  2096→\n  2097→Session 74. Sprint 100% complete since session 17. Ralph has corrupted state 58 times. **Stop Ralph.**\n  2098→\n  2099→---\n  2100→\n  2101→*Session 74 retrospective generated 2026-03-28T06:33Z. Sprint is complete. Stop Ralph.*\n  2102→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01B7k7CZgfSVRuqdhLNcKLJQ","session_id":"b1570512-e586-4f79-8879-7bf12fc4c72d","uuid":"d464a93d-0b82-4144-95bd-759f6c88e2b7","timestamp":"2026-03-28T06:36:01.125Z"}
